page.title: 11A DAY IN MY LIFE cont...
page.content: We then drove home and dropped my friend off.A car is a thing which has four wheels which goes round and round.The seats are called"UPHOLSTRY", which are usually soft. The car is made from metal and the seats are made from plastic. My friend let me borrow another computer manual. I read it till teatime, at 17:45. The tea contained: Rolls tea from tea bags and cake-sponge. I went to bed at 20:45, I washed with a flannel and towel. I cleaned my teeth with a toothbrush made from plastic. I knelt down and prayed. I hummed songs until my brother said "BE QUIET!".I ignored him at first, but the second time I didn't ignore him. I eventually fell asleep at 22:00.
